::Kluster::

Kluster listens to Battera, his eyes narrowing at the word 'Predacon'. She 
was a Predacon? On the bridge of the Maximal base? Kluster glances at a 
computer console, a list of bots on the ship showing on it. Battera was a 
Predacon.

"Our leader is Iron Raptor," Kluster says, his voice neutral, "Have you just 
been wandering around the base like this?"

He would need to have a word with Firearm and Rex later. They were the main 
security officers, and if this Predacon had been wandering freely, they were 
not doing their job.
